description: Sei que muitas de vocês tem dúvidas de como se vestir no verão – afinal, na maior parte do Brasil o calorzão da temporada é de nos fazer derreter ao longo do dia. Separei então várias dicas de looks de verão com 40 inspirações deusas vindas de várias fashionistas gringas e brazucas também. Para favoritar, salvar na sua pastinha de looks do Pinterest e se inspirar sempre que bater aquela dúvida de como se vestir nos dias mais quentes. Bora conferir? 5 dicas de como se vestir no verão: 1. Aposte em tecidos leves, confortáveis e preferencialmente de fibras naturais. Enquanto os tecidos sintéticos retém o calor, os tecidos com fibras naturais como os de algodão e os de linho permitem que a gente transpire melhor trazendo bem-estar nos dias de calorzão. With the coming of Spring, you know to expect that transitional period where it's not quite warm enough to go out with short sleeves and dresses, but not quite cold enough to wear a heavy coat. It's usually the best time to bring out your open-toe booties, lighter jackets, and brighter colors. I've got you covered on style inspiration on what to wear to transition to spring! T shirts are lightweight, making them extremely suitable for warm conditions. You may be keen for staff to look smart, but that shouldn’t be at the determent of their comfort. An uncomfortable employee is an unhappy one, and an unhappy one is unlikely to be productive. Plus, using T shirt printing, you can provide your employees with breathable, but branded workwear. title: 𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐲 𝐇𝐢𝐬
description: "Bella, pack your things and meet me in my car." He gritted out and turned around to walk out of my house. He can't just do this against my will. I take a deep breath and try again. "B-but I d-don't want t-to." I stutter quietly and immediately look down, regretting my words. He slowly, scarily turned around to face me and chuckled darkly. "But my love, you never had a choice." •••• Isabella Grace Lightwood. The definition of innocence. She's your typical 17 year old good and nice girl. Shy bookworm, perfect grades, doesn't party or sleep around with boys. She is completely clueless about things like make-up or boyfriends. She loves helping others and is kind to everyone. Leon Hunter Black. 19 years old. The definition of danger. He's the most feared guy in Bella's town and all over the world too. He has it all - money, good looks, power, you name it. Everyone is scared of him because of his dark appearance and his ruthless behaviour. Isabella is sure he is a cruel and heartless human. But is he really? What will happen when these two opposites cross paths? Everything is going to change when Bella catches the interest of the infamous Leon Black. But not everything is as bad as it seems... *** IT'S NOT THAT CLICHÉ, IT WILL GET BETTER!

name: d9aadd76b485e6dd3a2a642a6673a13c.jpg
title: Is This Family?
description: Katherine Jane, a simple and sweet loving girl. Everybody loves her....No. Nobody loves her. She always thought that if she gives love to everyone, everyone will love her. But she couldn't understand the harsh reality of the world. She was depressed and alone. Not to mention the constant verbal abuse from her mother. Yes, she has a birth mother but she doesn't care for her daughter. For her she is just a stomach she has to fill. Kat's only escape from this hateful world was her art. She is very smart and talented. Too pure for the world. The pain was excruciating and she was cracking under it. Until one day a knock on her door changes her life. But is it for good? Who knows... Turns out she has...brothers...6 of them. Disgustingly rich brothers. And they want to take her in. After a long time she sees hope. To be loved and taken care of. But she doesn't know she is in for another rejection and pain all over again. Will this rejection ever turn into love? Something she has never felt? Will she be able to win them? Or will they crush her until she finally gives up? Dive into the story of the Wright family. Get in for an emotional rollercoaster. One filled with pain towards love. Love. CONTAINS SWEARING.
